{"tid":161490,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加：過早被淘汰還不如踢歐霸盃","createTime":"2017-03-18T14:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T18:59:47.000Z","uid":43015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"44b5bff168b172c4038600d7ad9fda98b7ec3948","tid":161490,"uid":43015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:36:13.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴被摩納哥淘汰無緣歐聯8強，對於躊躇滿志的雲加而言，打擊是顯而易見的。在再次倒在16強後，「教授」甚至認為或許他的球隊參加歐霸盃更好。<br />\n<br />\n雲加已經連續率隊17個球季殺入歐聯，但近年來屢屢在淘汰賽首輪即提前出局，這讓雲加也感到十分沮喪。<br />\n<br />\n按照歐聯競賽規則，每個小組第3名的球隊，並非被直接淘汰出歐戰，而是有機會參加歐霸盃比賽，但阿仙奴卻從來沒有過這樣的經歷。在雲加看來，對於阿仙奴來說，或許在歐霸盃上槍手會有更好的奪冠機會。<br />\n<br />\n在被問及屢屢過早出局是否讓他感到煩惱時，雲加表示，「是的，但每次將我們淘汰的球隊，總能晉級最後的決賽。也許相比在歐聯16強戰中被淘汰，未能從小組出線，然後去踢歐霸盃會更好，那樣我們就有更多機會奪冠了。」<br />\n<br />\n雲加隨後解釋說，這只是對歐聯淘汰賽突然死亡本質的感慨，並不代表阿仙奴隊的野心和抱負真的發生了變化。"},{"pid":"ebec4f7d3aad5ed4a1502572576720f689d61278","tid":161490,"uid":70922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:37:38.000Z","msg":"10：2"},{"pid":"1c0401c2af15a896351d5ecc0b6c5442e08c142e","tid":161490,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:40:02.000Z","msg":"20:4"},{"pid":"1cf7391c2a2d81ec26969c061de95ec2fe84696d","tid":161490,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:40:52.000Z","msg":"歐霸盃？你諗多咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b922595c503a11aae044e3ba45d2fda354e7b314","tid":161490,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:45:23.000Z","msg":"所以爺爺今年唔搶第 4 諗住踢歐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b249df5211402c98ad1581aae9df8a5f7dc6ed0","tid":161490,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:45:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以爺爺今年唔搶第 4 諗住踢歐霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d5e61a9196829a117a93893ebfbfe9425c4f390b","tid":161490,"uid":16320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:47:38.000Z","msg":"西維爾對雲格讚好。"},{"pid":"f4bc2fe6943010a33974726a431b3bea252c906f","tid":161490,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:47:51.000Z","msg":"霸氣盃你都贏唔到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe574c5d3e17976e9bd0c9e935f5736c9105c46","tid":161490,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:48:20.000Z","msg":"最緊要踢多幾場有錢收"},{"pid":"4416995acdf3520e45859e951ba38849b0226024","tid":161490,"uid":13935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:51:36.000Z","msg":"咁天真以為自己贏到霸氣盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6741ab667b0f53028638adce935100dc8648fe0d","tid":161490,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T14:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee676203e4c98f23a86bac6ae0ef160b953ae300","tid":161490,"uid":43015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T18:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}